node.text:
#flashbackfriday To @nickcannon and #thejackson3 .... @themalikjackson @0ne0fone @_stak5_ 
I’ve been stewing since the latest unprovoked attack on my religion. My initial thoughts on this matter were very dark......so I held back.  I don’t freely offer my opinions especially in today’s society but enough is enough. I don’t have a military background but logic would tell me that one of the first rules of engagement is properly identifying your enemy. Please educate yourselves before you open your mouth. We are all in this together. You attack the Jewish people you attack me. Most Jewish people don’t look like me, don’t act like me and don’t respond like me and in a microcosm that is an example of a FLASHBACKFRIDAY 
Today is a new day and that mentality is old news. Get ready for a new normal. And just like @edelman11 said, we can all learn together. 👊 I’ll be the first to admit I don’t know everything BUT  I’m always willing to learn. There has to be a better way for us all 👊 👊👊 #proudjew #weareallinthistogether #donttreadonus #neverforget @wwe @dodgeofficial @mitchalbom @haimgozali ..... this ones for you 👊 #spear #jackhammer #whosnext 🇺🇸🇮🇱
